<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>Clone<sp/>an<sp/>existing<sp/>GameObject<sp/>(copies<sp/>all<sp/>Cloneable<sp/>components)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">auto<sp/>prototype<sp/>=<sp/>GameObjectFactory::from(existingGameObject);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>GameObjectPrototype</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
